    "body": "Add the following to your starship.toml\n```\n[env_var.flox_env]\nvariable = \"FLOX_PROMPT_ENVIRONMENTS\"\nformat = \"[$env_value]($style) \"\nstyle = \"bold blue\"\n```\nThen for your starship's base format you need to make sure it contains `${env_var.flox_env}`",
